{"tid":83958,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【公院性侵】13歲男童 遭同房42歲男病人性侵","createTime":"2017-01-17T07:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T11:04:38.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"27a1ce31dd58741c6324e5beff53f155c0d930a8","tid":83958,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T07:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170117/large/1484636245_029d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170117%2Flarge%2F1484636245_029d.jpg&h=2e935e31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼九龍醫院爆出集體性侵犯病人案後，再有公立醫院發生同類事件。聯合醫院一名13歲男童，去年12月中起留院精神科病房。其間被一名42歲同房病人要求協助手淫。男童於本月4日才向家人透露事件，家人隨即報警。警方經調查後，昨日拘捕該名42歲男子，他涉嫌向年齡在16歲以下的兒童作出猥褻行為。被捕男子現正被扣留調查。案件由秀茂坪警區重案組第一隊跟進。"},{"pid":"e21614a8a85c1315f7d91d09dc81743e604646ec","tid":83958,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T08:33:58.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"87b6dd239da260bea064d2c23d775ad964f60513","tid":83958,"uid":17984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T08:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3a791c76ac96fd71adf0f95532306265008acc","tid":83958,"uid":39381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T08:38:55.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n精神科冇兒童病房？點解會有43歲同房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef64fcc6a748b1d3a87d7c618792ec686490a02","tid":83958,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e988e58c1876a4b72669005f184b89eab85022e